<tr><td><font face="Comic Sans MS" size=2><font color=#800000><a name=0></a><b><br>We sell an Everquest accaunt</b></font><font color=#006600 size=1> [ <a href=mailto:eq_trade@usa.net target=main><font color=#006600>ShadowMaster</font></a> at 08:01 CST ]</font></font></tr></td>
<tr><td><font face="Comic Sans MS" size=2>Check here for details: <a href="http://cgi.ebay.com/aw-cgi/eBayISAPI.dll?ViewItem&item=402319669" target="_blank">56 level cleric!</a><br><br>Thanks!</font></td></tr>
